##Installing ProtGPS

##Clone the ProtGPS Github repository in the root directory

git clone https://github.com/pgmikhael/protgps.git
cd protgps
mamba env create -f environment.yml

##Downloading model checkpoints from Zenodo in the ProtGPS folder
wget https://zenodo.org/records/14795445/files/checkpoints.zip?download=1
ls protgps/checkpoints/protgps/ #extract the checkpoints to checkpoints/protgps
